title: Franz Ferdinand - BBC Big Weekend [Video Album[
description:
Music Videos downsampled to 720P HD for maximum compatibility with professional DJ software such as Ots DJ Pro which often lacks full HD support due to the ability to scratch Video tracks and also often do not fully support the importation of ULTRA HD or even full HD Video formats such as MP4 and MKV.

Audio is 320kbps at 48 KHz quality.  Source BBC, thank you to the original seed on demonoid for this wonderful 4 day music festival.
